ABOUT YOUR HEIGHT,

21:49.220 --> 21:51.527
VERY, VERY THIN.

21:51.658 --> 21:53.007
-I COULD FIND
THAT GUY MYSELF.

21:53.137 --> 21:54.530
-YEAH, LEAVE IT,
IT'S OVER, HUH?

21:54.661 --> 21:56.010
-SHE COULD'VE
GOT KILLED, MITCH.

21:56.140 --> 21:57.751
-WELL, SHE HANDLED
HERSELF LIKE A PRO.

21:58.578 --> 21:59.796
-THAT'S ABOUT ALL
I CAN TELL YOU.

21:59.927 --> 22:00.797
