RIGHT INTO THE LOT

22:11.025 --> 22:12.069
BEFORE WE EVER
GOT TO THE BEACH.

22:12.200 --> 22:13.984
-IMPORTANT THING
IS YOU'RE OKAY.

22:14.115 --> 22:16.030
YOU KEPT YOUR COOL
AND YOU'RE NOT HURT.

22:16.160 --> 22:17.205
-NO, NO, NO, NO,
HE DROPPED HIS GUN.

22:17.336 --> 22:18.337
I COULDA HAD HIM!

22:20.121 --> 22:21.122
-COME ON. I'LL
TAKE YA HOME.

22:23.516 --> 22:25.126
-POLICE SAID IF THEY
FIND OUT ANYTHING,

22:25.256 --> 22:26.170
THEY'LL LET
US KNOW, HUH?

22:37.878 --> 22:38.879
-IS EVERYTHING
OKAY IN HERE?

22:42.056 --> 22:43.100
-FINE.

22:52.632 --> 22:53.459
-[EXHALES]

23:11.781 --> 23:13.348
-YA KNOW, I THINK
I SHOULD CALL

23:13.479 --> 23:14.610
AND SEE IF THEY'VE
HEARD ANYTHING.

23:15.437 --> 23:17.396
-THEY SAID THEY'D
LET US KNOW.

23:19.049 --> 23:20.181
IF THEY CATCH THE GUY.

23:23.097 --> 23:23.967
OKAY?

23:30.887 --> 23:31.671
CAROLINE.

23:31.801 --> 23:32.628
-WHAT?

23:37.241 --> 23:39.069
-WHEN I THINK ABOUT
WHAT COULD HAVE HAPPENED,

23:43.596 --> 23:44.858
I JUST WANT
YOU TO BE SAFE.

23:45.728 --> 23:46.642
-I KNOW.

23:49.732 --> 23:51.299
BUT I GUESS IT CAN'T
ALWAYS WORK THAT WAY.

23:53.519 --> 23:55.129
I MEAN, EITHER ONE
OF US COULD GET HURT

23:55.259 --> 23:56.347
DOING WHAT WE DO.

23:58.175 --> 24:00.047
BUT I FIGURE THERE'S MORE
OF A CHANCE OF ME GETTING

24:00.177 --> 24:02.005
INTO A CAR WRECK
ON THE WAY TO WORK

24:02.136 --> 24:03.180
THAN SOME CRAZY
GUY WITH A GUN

24:03.311 --> 24:04.617
EVER DOING THAT
TO ME AGAIN.

24:07.794 --> 24:09.970
I GUESS I JUST CAN'T
STAY COOPED UP IN MY ROOM

24:10.100 --> 24:13.190
FOR THE REST OF MY LIFE
BECAUSE SOMETHING MIGHT HAPPEN

24:13.321 --> 24:14.627
OUT THERE IN THE
BIG, BAD WORLD.

24:14.757 --> 24:15.628
-I KNOW.

24:18.108 --> 24:19.109
COME ON, GET
SOME SLEEP.

24:26.987 --> 24:27.814
WELCOME HOME.

24:29.990 --> 24:33.559
-[SOFT MUSIC]

24:36.387 --> 24:38.868
-CAROLINE, WAKE
UP. WAKE UP!

24:42.176 --> 24:43.438
WAKE UP SLEEPYHEAD.

24:52.229 --> 24:53.448
HAVE A GOOD DAY!

25:03.197 --> 25:06.635
-HI! YA KNOW, YOU REALLY
SHOULD WATCH WHERE YOU'RE GOING.

25:06.766 --> 25:10.378
-[SCREAMING]

25:12.206 --> 25:13.816
NO! NO!

25:13.947 --> 25:15.339
-CAROLINE.

25:15.470 --> 25:16.950
-NO! GET AWAY FROM
ME. GET AWAY FROM ME!

25:17.080 --> 25:18.125
-IT'S ME! IT'S JD!

25:18.255 --> 25:18.952
-[GASPING]
-JD: IT'S ME.

25:19.082 --> 25:20.257
-OH GOD.

25:20.388 --> 25:21.128
-YOU HAD A BAD
DREAM. IT'S OKAY.

25:21.258 --> 25:22.477
-IT WAS HIM. I SAW HIM.

25:22.608 --> 25:23.696
HE WAS ON MY TOWER.

25:25.698 --> 25:29.266
-IT'S OKAY. YOU'RE
SAFE NOW, ALL RIGHT?

25:30.877 --> 25:33.488
IT'S OKAY.
IT'S OKAY.

25:37.753 --> 25:38.754
SHHH...

25:40.321 --> 25:41.496
YOU'RE SAFE NOW.

25:44.281 --> 25:46.719
-MITCH: YOU WERE IN THE WRONG
PLACE AT THE WRONG TIME.

25:46.849 --> 25:48.677
IT WAS BAD LUCK. LOOK,
HE'S NOT COMIN' BACK.

25:48.808 --> 25:50.287
-I KNOW.

25:50.418 --> 25:52.202
-HE'S PROBABLY HALFWAY
TO GUADALAJARA BY NOW.

25:52.333 --> 25:53.682
-YOU'RE RIGHT.

25:53.813 --> 25:55.205
-OKAY, YOU WANT A
LIFT TO YOUR TOWER?

25:56.032 --> 25:57.773
-NO! COME
ON, I'M FINE.

25:57.904 --> 25:59.514
-ALL RIGHT. SEE YA.

