28:46.202 --> 28:47.813
-I'LL PICK IT
UP AFTER WORK.

28:48.552 --> 28:49.597
-YOU OKAY?

28:49.728 --> 28:50.772
-YEAH. I'M FINE.

28:51.860 --> 28:53.296
-SO, WHAT TIME IS
YOUR SHIFT OVER?

28:53.427 --> 28:55.081
-5:30.

28:55.211 --> 28:57.257
I'LL SWING BY AND PICK UP
THE CHECK ON MY WAY HOME.

28:57.387 --> 28:59.346
-GREAT. SEE YA AT 5:30.

29:00.086 --> 29:01.827
-[SLOW MUSIC]

29:12.054 --> 29:12.968
-WHAT TIME IS IT?

29:13.664 --> 29:14.927
-ALMOST SIX.

29:15.057 --> 29:16.972
SHE'S SCARED
AND PARANOID.

29:17.103 --> 29:18.234
I BET SHE'S
NOT EVEN COMING.

29:18.365 --> 29:21.020
-[GROANING]

29:21.150 --> 29:22.586
-HEY!

29:22.717 --> 29:24.023
TAYLOR TOLD ME I COULD
FIND YA DOWN HERE.

29:24.588 --> 29:26.329
SHE DIDN'T KNOW ANYTHING
ABOUT MY DISABILITY CHECK.

29:26.460 --> 29:27.722
-YEAH I KNOW, SORRY.

29:27.853 --> 29:28.941
I MADE THAT UP.

29:30.072 --> 29:32.901
WE NEED TO HAVE A
LITTLE TALK. IN PRIVATE.

29:34.903 --> 29:35.817
-I DON'T UNDERSTAND.

29:36.600 --> 29:37.471
WHAT'S GOIN' ON?

29:40.039 --> 29:41.780
-I TOLD MITCH, NEELY.

29:43.216 --> 29:43.999
-TOLD HIM WHAT?

29:44.130 --> 29:44.913
-ABOUT.

29:45.044 --> 29:46.393
-ABOUT YOUR PROBLEM.

29:46.523 --> 29:47.916
-PROBLEM?

29:48.047 --> 29:49.483
I DON'T HAVE A PROBLEM.

29:49.613 --> 29:50.919
-NEELY.

29:51.050 --> 29:52.355
-I SAID I DON'T
HAVE A PROBLEM.

29:52.486 --> 29:53.443
I GOTTA GO.

29:53.574 --> 29:54.793
-NO. NO, PLEASE STAY.

29:54.923 --> 29:56.272
-YOU? YOU'RE MY FRIEND?

29:56.403 --> 29:58.274
-YES, SHE IS YOUR
FRIEND AND SO AM I.

29:58.405 --> 29:59.754
WE WANNA TRY
TO HELP YOU HERE.

29:59.885 --> 30:01.321
-I DON'T NEED HELP.

30:01.451 --> 30:02.931
-YOU'RE ADDICTED
TO PAIN PILLS.

30:03.802 --> 30:05.020
-NO, I'M NOT.

30:05.151 --> 30:07.022
-NEELY, NEELY, WE
CAN HELP YOU.

30:07.153 --> 30:09.024
YOU'VE JUST GOTTA
TAKE THE FIRST STEP.

30:09.895 --> 30:11.244
-MITCH.

30:11.374 --> 30:12.549
-NEELY, I CALLED THE
HOSPITAL IN ASPEN.

30:12.680 --> 30:13.812
THERE'S NO
RECORD OF YOU HAVING

30:13.942 --> 30:15.117
ANY KIND OF
TREATMENT AT ALL.

30:15.248 --> 30:16.771
YOU DIDN'T HURT
YOUR BACK SKIING.

30:16.902 --> 30:17.946
-WELL YOU MUST HAVE
CALLED THE WRONG HOSPITAL.

30:18.077 --> 30:19.905
-LET'S NOT GO
FOR GAMES, OKAY?

30:20.035 --> 30:21.341
THE GUY ON THE FIREWORKS BARGE
COULD'VE DIED BECAUSE OF YOU.

30:21.471 --> 30:22.342
-WELL, HE DIDN'T.

30:22.472 --> 30:23.734
-THE NEXT ONE MIGHT.

30:25.780 --> 30:28.348
LOOK, YOU ARE UNFIT
TO BE A LIFEGUARD.

30:28.478 --> 30:29.697
NOW, IF YOU DON'T
TELL THE SUPERVISOR

30:29.828 --> 30:31.394
AT THE SAND
AND SEA, I WILL.

30:31.525 --> 30:32.918
-YOU'D GET ME FIRED?

30:33.048 --> 30:34.789
-YES! I WILL IF IT
HELPS YOU GET BETTER.

30:34.920 --> 30:36.791
LOOK, YOU NEED TIME TO
DEAL WITH YOUR PROBLEM.

30:36.922 --> 30:38.358
-YOU CAN'T DO
THIS TO ME!

30:41.187 --> 30:42.797
IF I LOSE MY JOB, I...

30:45.278 --> 30:46.192
I CAN'T.

30:46.322 --> 30:47.541
-YOU CAN'T WHAT, NEELY?

30:48.977 --> 30:50.413
-I CAN'T TAKE
CARE OF HER.

30:51.153 --> 30:52.328
-TAKE CARE OF WHO?

30:55.897 --> 30:56.855
-MY BABY.

31:01.424 --> 31:02.643
I DIDN'T HURT MY BACK.

31:05.080 --> 31:06.342
I HAD A BABY.

31:09.302 --> 31:10.172
ASHLEY.

31:14.481 --> 31:17.876
-HOW'D YOU GET ADDICTED TO
PAIN PILLS WITH A LITTLE BABY?

31:22.576 --> 31:24.621
-THE DELIVERY WAS HARD.

31:24.752 --> 31:27.450
I WAS ALONE AND AFRAID.

31:28.016 --> 31:30.192
I KEPT CRYING
ALL THE TIME.

31:32.020 --> 31:34.893
SO, I STARTED TAKING
THEM TO FEEL BETTER.

31:37.504 --> 31:40.159
AND I COULDN'T STOP.

31:44.467 --> 31:45.425
-WHERE IS SHE?

31:46.817 --> 31:48.080
-SHE'S WITH MY MOTHER.

31:49.733 --> 31:51.953
SHE COULDN'T LIVE WITH
ME, NOT THE WAY I AM NOW.

31:53.737 --> 31:56.044
ASHLEY, SHE
DOESN'T NEED ME.

31:59.787 --> 32:00.962
I'M NOT A GOOD MOM.

32:08.143 --> 32:09.884
-HEY, COME
HERE, COME HERE.

32:13.279 --> 32:14.584
LET ME TELL
YA A LITTLE STORY.

32:16.630 --> 32:19.285
WHEN HOBIE WAS ABOUT
THREE MONTHS OLD,

32:20.547 --> 32:23.245
HIS MOM AND I, WE
HAD AN ARGUMENT.

32:24.072 --> 32:25.682
MUST HAVE BEEN A
PRETTY STUPID ARGUMENT

32:25.813 --> 32:27.336
'CAUSE I CAN'T REMEMBER
WHAT IT WAS ABOUT.

32:28.250 --> 32:30.557
BUT, WHAT I DO
REMEMBER IS THAT

32:30.687 --> 32:32.951
GAYLE TOOK HOBIE TO
HER MOTHER'S HOUSE

32:34.517 --> 32:36.650
AND THEY WERE GONE
FOR THREE MONTHS.

32:38.260 --> 32:41.263
AND AT THAT
MOMENT, I REALIZED

32:42.177 --> 32:43.570
THAT I WAS A DAD.

32:44.875 --> 32:45.746
YOU KNOW WHY?

32:46.573 --> 32:48.836
BECAUSE I REALLY
NEEDED HOBIE.

32:50.055 --> 32:51.230
AND HE NEEDED ME.

32:53.058 --> 32:56.148
AND BELIEVE ME,
THAT LITTLE GIRL

32:57.192 --> 32:58.019
NEEDS YOU.

33:00.195 --> 33:01.370
SO, WHAT I'M SAYIN' IS,

33:02.719 --> 33:04.852
YOU GOTTA GET
BETTER, RIGHT?

33:05.592 --> 33:06.941
NOT JUST FOR YOURSELF,

33:08.464 --> 33:10.727
BUT FOR THAT LITTLE
GIRL NAMED ASHLEY.

33:12.686 --> 33:13.600
OKAY?

33:17.996 --> 33:19.040
I KNOW.

33:37.537 --> 33:38.712
-HEY, DONNA.

33:39.669 --> 33:41.019
-IF YOU'RE
LOOKING FOR NEELY,

33:41.149 --> 33:42.107
I HAVEN'T SEEN HER
ANYWHERE NEAR THE CLUB.

33:42.759 --> 33:44.152
-I JUST TALKED
TO THE MANAGER.

33:44.283 --> 33:45.980
HE SAID SHE ASKED FOR
A LEAVE OF ABSENCE.

33:46.502 --> 33:47.503
PERSONAL PROBLEMS.

33:47.634 --> 33:48.852
-WHERE'D SHE GO?

33:48.983 --> 33:50.115
-NO IDEA.

33:50.245 --> 33:50.767
-DONNA: WELL,
WHAT DO WE DO?

33:51.420 --> 33:53.509
-WAIT. NOTHING
ELSE WE CAN DO.

33:54.119 --> 33:55.381
NEXT MOVE'S UP TO NEELY.

33:55.990 --> 33:56.860
SEE YA.

34:02.866 --> 34:05.173
-[SOFT MUSIC]

34:10.004 --> 34:13.616
-[LIVELY MUSIC]

34:15.139 --> 34:19.187
♪ I WAS ASHAMED OF WHO I COULDN'T BE

34:23.364 --> 34:27.195
