37:11.751 --> 37:13.535
-NO, NO, NO, CAROLINE!
STAY IN THE TRUCK!

37:13.666 --> 37:14.884
CAROLINE!

37:15.972 --> 37:18.453
-[INTENSE MUSIC]

37:22.065 --> 37:23.502
