37:23.632 --> 37:24.546
-CAROLINE!

37:25.591 --> 37:29.769
-[INTENSE MUSIC]

37:33.860 --> 37:35.122
-CAROLINE: HEY! STOP!

37:37.994 --> 37:40.258
-JD: CAROLINE!
WAIT! STOP!

37:41.476 --> 37:44.000
-[INTENSE MUSIC]

37:49.658 --> 37:52.052
-[CROWD CHATTERS]

37:54.533 --> 37:55.751
JD: CAROLINE!

37:57.231 --> 37:58.450
CAROLINE!

37:59.407 --> 38:00.756
STAY BACK.
I'LL GET HIM.

38:02.192 --> 38:04.934
-[INTENSE MUSIC]

38:35.704 --> 38:37.053
-[GRUNTING]

38:39.317 --> 38:41.449
-MITCH: ALL RIGHT,
JD. CALL THE COPS.

38:41.580 --> 38:44.017
-OH MY GOD.
IT'S NOT HIM.

38:44.147 --> 38:45.018
-WHAT?

38:45.540 --> 38:46.541
-I'M SORRY.

38:47.194 --> 38:47.977
I'M SO SORRY.

38:48.108 --> 38:49.631
-IT'S THE WRONG GUY?

39:02.731 --> 39:05.473
THEY CAUGHT A GUY MATCHING
THE DESCRIPTION YOU GAVE

39:05.604 --> 39:07.432
TRYING TO CROSS OVER
THE MEXICAN BORDER

39:07.562 --> 39:08.607
IN A STOLEN CAR.

39:09.782 --> 39:12.741
THEY WANT YOU TO COME IN
TOMORROW TO IDENTIFY HIM.

39:13.481 --> 39:14.352
-OKAY.

39:16.702 --> 39:18.007
YOU KNOW I CAN
STILL SEE HIM.

39:19.792 --> 39:22.490
I CAN STILL FEEL HIM
STANDING RIGHT BEHIND ME.

39:23.839 --> 39:24.710
-I KNOW.

39:26.712 --> 39:28.235
IT'S NOT GONNA
LAST FOREVER.

39:30.150 --> 39:31.804
-I WAS THINKING ABOUT
GOING BACK TO NEW YORK.

39:32.892 --> 39:34.372
TRY AND PUT THIS
ALL BEHIND ME.

39:35.808 --> 39:37.157
-BUT YOU'RE
NOT GOING TO.

39:39.812 --> 39:42.162
-I FIGURE, LET THIS
GUY CHASE ME AWAY

39:42.292 --> 39:44.207
