41:27.615 --> 41:28.834
YEAH.

41:28.964 --> 41:29.965
-HI, SWEETHEART.

41:31.401 --> 41:33.447
-WELCOME TO
BAYWATCH, ASHLEY.

41:34.492 --> 41:35.754
-NEELY: YES.

